.ends


* expanding   symbol:  sg13g2_tests/inv_sweep_tb.sym # of pins=0
** sym_path: /home/tulpar/vlsi/pdk/ihp-sg13g2/libs.tech/xschem/sg13g2_tests/inv_sweep_tb.sym
